You can now create new A, MX and CNAME records on the domains from the client portal.

**DNS Manager**

Log-in to the Client Portal.
Go to Menu >> DNS
Click on the Domain name you want to create new DNS entries.
You can create new MX record, A record, A record on Subdomains and CNAME records on subdomains.

**Create New MX Records**

- From the DNS manager click on MX
- Enter the new MX hostname and select the priority from the next drop down list
- Then click on the OK button

**Create A Records**

- From the DNS manager click on A
- You can change the primary A record of your website and also change the subdomains A record
